\exe I felt like we could find something just watching each other.
\exsrc VAL159
\ex Tubiŋsi ghari nikani lusi, rettine, cektine.
\exe When we have met let's get to know each other, let's laugh and talk.
\exsrc VAL161
\ex  Huŋgo khalko sahayog pikapi lusikiya teĩbe.
\exe We give that kind of help to each other in the village.
\exsrc VAL162
\qst

