\exsrc field notes ROS
\se lamma kaiʔma
\des have.an.appetite.for; be.keen.on; desire; feel.tempted.by
\gns मन पराउनु; चाहा गर्नु
\ex Huĩ suncuwace alamma kattoŋsuce.
