\lg C
\ex Arko thitta sakpha kondukuŋ.
\exe I'm looking for one other bamboo stick.
\exn अर्को एउटा बाँस खोज्छु ।
\exsrc CLLDCh4R02S04.138
\ex Maʔmiŋa cha kondose.
\exe The man has searched for the child.
