\lex kond
\ct koĩma
\morph koĩ
\morph kon
\ps vi
\mtyp stem
\val [A-ERG O-NOM] S-INF V-s(S); A-ERG O-NOM INF V-s(O); [S-NOM] S-INF V-s(S)
\de must; should; have.to
\gn चाहिनु; गर्नु पर्नु
\lg C
\ex Caha linogo asuk sambok ucuʔnulok sopma konno.
\exe The required amount of millet has to be husked.
\exn चाहिने जति कोदो राम्ररी खल्नु पर्छ ।
\exsrc thi_numma.15
\ex Cuwa lokto pache choku cimtaŋa lapma kina tima konnoʔ.
\exe After the water comes to a boil one has to take the nettles with pincers and put them in.
\exsrc VAL120
\ex Bago Malesia haŋma konno.
\exe This one must be sent to Malaysia.
\exsrc VAL150
\ex Cuwa tima kina lokmeiʔma konno.
\exe One has to fill in water and boil it.
\exsrc VAL176
\com the embedded clause normally behaves like S of the embedded verb; embedded P/T/G linked to O-AGR may raise to matrix S-AGR
\qst

