\mtyp stem
\val A-ERG O-NOM INF V-a(A).o(O); A-NOM P-INF V-a(A).o(P); A-ERG P-INF V-a(A).o(P); A-NOM P-INF V-s(A)
\de stop.to; suffice.to
\gn रोक्नु
\lg C
\com shares P/T/G with embedded transitive verb, takes embedded intransitive verb as full P if the action is volitional and as faded P if the action is non-volitional. The alternation between intransitive/non-volitional and transitive/volitional resembles that found with kond- 'want'. 
