\lex sameiʔ
\alt same
\ps n
\mtyp stem
\de protoclan
\seme Rais in Chintang and elsewhere do not only belong to a clan (pacha) but also to a protoclan (sameiʔ), which is a larger unit usually comprising several clans. Differently from clans, however, there are separate protoclans for males and females, so brothers and sisters belong to different protoclans.
\gn गोत्र
\semn छिन्ताङ र अन्य ठाउँका राईहरूको जातको कुरा गर्दा उनिहरूको विभाजन पाछामा मात्र नभइ सामेइ:मा पनि हुन्छ । धेरै पाछाहरूको एउटै सामेइ: र महिला र पुरुषको अलग-अलग सामेइ: हुन्छ ।
