\des then; after.that
\gns त्यसपछि
\se utti panta
\des then; so; in.that.case
\gns त्यसो भए
\ex Utti panta apaisa na hende.
\exe I can save my money, then.
\exn त्यसो भए मेरो पैँसा त बच्यो ।
\exsrc CLLDCh1R04S02. 531
\se utti para
\des then; so; in.that.case
\gns त्यसो भए
\ex E, utti para hani na saber ta ataicaihẽ ni?
\exe So you came early in the morning?
\exn ए, त्यसो भए तिमीहरू त सबेरै आईहाल्यौ नि ?
\exsrc them_talk.073
\qst

